sync" class="size-full wp-image-3787542" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/OASIS_REUNION_PHOTO_1_LANDSCAPE.jpg" alt="Liam 和 Noel Gallagher 终于聚在一起，为 2025 年英国和爱尔兰体育场巡演的 Oasis 重聚。图片来源：Simon Emmett" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/OASIS_REUNION_PHOTO_1_LANDSCAPE.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/OASIS_REUNION_PHOTO_1_LANDSCAPE-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/OASIS_REUNION_PHOTO_1_LANDSCAPE-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/OASIS_REUNION_PHOTO_1_LANDSCAPE-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/OASIS_REUNION_PHOTO_1_LANDSCAPE-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/OASIS_REUNION_PHOTO_1_LANDSCAPE-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3787542" class="wp-caption-text"> Liam 和 Noel Gallagher 终于聚在一起，为 2025 年英国和爱尔兰体育场巡演的 Oasis 重聚。图片来源：Simon Emmett</figcaption></figure><p>还提供一系列价格较高的招待、粉丝和商品套餐。 <a href="https://www.gigsandtours.com/tour/oasis?src=mk_hptakeover-oasis-27-08-24&amp;utm_source=GigsandTours&amp;utm_medium=website&amp;utm_campaign=hptakeover-oasis-27-08-24" target="_blank" rel="noopener">请访问此处了解更多信息</a>。</p><p>在其他地方， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-reunion-tour-ticket-prices-revealed-for-dublin-other-shows-expected-to-follow-3788631">已确认都柏林演出的起价为 86.50 欧元</a>。</p><p> Oasis 2025 年英国和爱尔兰巡演门票于本周六（8 月 31 日）上午 9 点（英国夏令时）/上午 8 点（美国标准时间）开始全面发售 - <a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fsearch%3Fq%3Doasis" target="_blank" rel="noopener">您可以在这里</a>（英国）和<a href="https://ticketmaster.evyy.net/c/2862475/264167/4272?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.ie%2Fsearch%3Fq%3Doasis" target="_blank" rel="noopener">这里</a>（爱尔兰）购买门票。粉丝们还可以在英国夏令时间昨晚（28 日）晚上 7 点之前<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-share-deta